{"type": "article", "id": 27402, "title": "隐形的书架", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-27T06:54:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 227, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171738z9JpgEG2DihcdP6q.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>想让书像是被施展了魔法那样“悬浮”起来？Miron Lior 为家具品牌 umbra 设计的隐形书架会让拜访你家的客人大吃一惊。书架呈字母 L 造型，水平端下方隐藏的小钩可以夹住最下面的一本书的封底，固定之后就可以把书往上摆了。根据不同的尺寸，最高可以承受 13 千克的重量。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.umbra.com/usd/wall-decor/shelves-boards/conceal-floating-shelf-collection\">购买链接</a>，售价从 13 到 18 美元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171736cVZryWRefBLGdOHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171737efUSHY0gZvbtAp1o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171737X6TNHG4kDMoe7x3K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}